    "For example, a manipulative real-estate agent may use the homely scent of freshly baked cookies at a house viewing to lure in potential buyers who, nonetheless, are be fully aware that they are being manipulated (Barnhill, 2014).",
    "Similarly, the dark pattern known as a 'roach motel' often prevents users from cancelling a service by making it cumbersome and tiring to complete (Brignull, 2023).",
